Fidelcor Inc's Fidelcor Business CreditCorp subsidiary said it reached a definitive agreement toacquire a substantial portion of the Bank of New England Corp's&lt;BKNE> Lazere Financial Corp's assets.    Terms of the acquisition were not disclosed. Theacquisition is subject to approval of the Federal ReserveBoard.    Fidelcor said it would acquire most of Lazere's loanportfolio and other assets, including its Miami office. It saidit plans to hire the majority of Lazere's 100 employees. Reuter&#3;